{"_path":"/city/t043","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"身心障礙者～營養餐飲服務","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t043-1.jpeg","sequence":43,"category":"身障營養餐費補助","author":"桃園市社會局","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/15gj2HwY6y/","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"身心障礙者營養餐飲服務"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"身心障礙者～營養餐飲服務"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為能夠更即時關心身心障礙者～\n桃園市府提供 👉🏻 每日送營養餐飲服務 🥣"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n期盼透過送餐方式，能夠具體了解身障者的生活狀況及服務需求，必要時還可以提供幫助，讓我們多出一份力，關心社會弱勢族群、獨居長者 ❤️"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 身障者餐飲補助，每日最多補助 2 餐，每餐最高補助$90💰，一天最高可補助$180💰 唷！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 身心障礙營養餐費補助對象："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n只要居住在桃園市並符合長照需要等級 2 至 8 級，以及符合長照中低收入戶和領取身心障礙生活補助者，並符合以下之一有餐飲服務需求者："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1️⃣65 歲以上獨居老人且無法自行炊食或外出購餐者。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2️⃣55 歲以上獨居原住民且無法自行炊食或外出購餐者。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3️⃣15 歲以上領有身心障礙證明者，且獨居無法自行炊食或外出購餐者；非獨居但無法自行炊食或外出購餐，且家人也無法提供餐食者。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n想了解更多桃園身障者餐飲補助內容，請至桃園市政府"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sab.tycg.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=7325&s=1001172"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" 社會局網站查詢 "}]},{"type":"text","value":"🔍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t043-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t043-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"身心障礙者營養餐飲服務","depth":2,"text":"身心障礙者～營養餐飲服務"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t043.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t043.md","_extension":"md"}